HEADWORD: Blockhead
<hw>Block"head`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Block</ets> + <ets>head</ets>.]</ety> <def>A stupid fellow; a
dolt; a person deficient in understanding.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The bookful <qex>blockhead</qex>, ignorantly read,⟦br⟧
With loads of learned lumber in his head.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blockheaded</ent>⟦br⟧
